27
00:01:08,120 --> 00:01:09,480
Meng is the best.

28
00:01:15,440 --> 00:01:16,480
Is it good?

29
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:17,280
Yes.

30
00:01:22,440 --> 00:01:23,200
What's wrong?

31
00:01:23,960 --> 00:01:24,920
Xuan Pei,

32
00:01:25,880 --> 00:01:27,280
