33
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:29,560
I want to sleep.

34
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:32,760
The rose in the cake is made of wine.

35
00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:33,960
You've never drunk wine.

36
00:01:33,960 --> 00:01:34,720
It's your first time.

37
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:35,880
You'll feel dizzy.

38
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:39,280
Come here.

39
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:40,320
Lie down for a while.

40
00:01:40,320 --> 00:01:41,280
You'll feel better.

41
00:01:45,520 --> 00:01:48,600
I'm feeling dizzy.

42
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:51,200
You'll feel drunk.

43
00:01:52,600 --> 00:01:53,840
Drunk?

44
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:56,400
What's drunk?

45
00:01:57,880 --> 00:01:58,840
Anyway,

46
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,160
it's not a good thing.

47
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:02,640
Stay away from it.

48
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:06,440
Stay away from whom?

49
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:07,280
No.

50
00:02:07,880 --> 00:02:11,280
I want to be with Xuan Pei forever.

51
00:02:11,720 --> 00:02:13,800
You're drunk after drinking so much.

52
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,840
It seems that you can't run away from it.

53
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:22,840
Who are you?

54
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:25,800
I'm your Xuan Pei.

55
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:26,840
Xuan Pei?

56
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:29,040
Xuan Pei,

57
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:34,640
