58
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:38,640
Honeycomb cake.

59
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:44,080
What's your favorite book?

60
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:47,600
Xiong Yuan Bao and his friends.

61
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:53,320
It's all the children of Jiuyou who read it.

62
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:54,840
Because I want to investigate

63
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:56,020
the most popular flamespot

64
00:02:56,020 --> 00:02:57,940
in Jiuyou Youth

65
00:02:57,940 --> 00:02:59,840
thatuck opening and closing of the sandwich as a subject.

66
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:01,960
Then...

67
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:05,760
who

68
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:11,400
is your favorite?

69
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:17,720
It's always you.

70
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:25,520
Hurry up.

71
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:26,640
Let's go.

72
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:33,960
