75
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,360
After you get your job?

76
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:39,960
What do you mean?

77
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:40,960
Think about it.

78
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:43,120
